When asked by reporters about China and India's purchase of Russian oil, the White House bluntly exposed its duplicity. As is known, the U.S. government has long been adept at playing double standards on various issues such as democracy and human rights. Editor: Yuan Xin Chief editor: Ge Jing Managing director: Mei Yan (To submit cartoons and share story ideas or feedback on our cartoon page, please contact us at cartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)